 %% ===== STRATEGY PATTERN - Projectile Effects =====
 class IProjectileEffect {
 <<interface>>
 +ApplyEffect(enemy, bullet)
 }
 
 class FireEffect {
 +ApplyEffect(enemy, bullet)
 }
 
 class IceEffect {
 +ApplyEffect(enemy, bullet)
 }
 
 IProjectileEffect <|.. FireEffect
 IProjectileEffect <|.. IceEffect

 %% ===== STATE PATTERN - Enemy States =====
 class IEnemyState {
 <<interface>>
 +Enter(enemy)
 +Update(enemy)
 +Exit(enemy)
 }
 
 class NormalState {
 +Enter(enemy)
 +Update(enemy)
 +Exit(enemy)
 }
 
 class BurnedState {
 -float duration
 -float burnDamage
 +Enter(enemy)
 +Update(enemy)
 +Exit(enemy)
 }
 
 IEnemyState <|.. NormalState
 IEnemyState <|.. BurnedState

 %% ===== DECORATOR PATTERN - Bullet Visuals =====
 class IBulletVisualDecorator {
 <<interface>>
 +ApplyVisual(bullet)
 }
 
 class FireBulletVisualDecorator {
 +ApplyVisual(bullet)
 }
 
 IBulletVisualDecorator <|.. FireBulletVisualDecorator

 %% ===== FACTORY PATTERN - Tower Creation =====
 class TowerFactory {
 <<static>>
 +CreateTower(type, position)
 +GetTowerCost(type)
 }
 
 class TowerType {
 <<enumeration>>
 Fire
 Ice
 Wind
 Basic
 }
 
 TowerFactory --> TowerType

 %% ===== SINGLETON PATTERN - Game Managers =====
 class GameManager {
 <<Singleton>>
 +static Instance
 +Money
 +Lives
 +EnemyKilled(enemy)
 +GameOver()
 }
 
 class EnemyManagerScript {
 <<Singleton>>
 +static Instance
 +RegisterEnemy(enemy)
 +GetEnemyInRange(position, range)
 }
 
 class Pool {
 <<Singleton>>
 +static Instance
 +ActivateObject(tag)
 +DeactivateObject(item)
 }

 %% ===== CORE GAME CLASSES =====
 class EnemyScript {
 +float Health
 -IEnemyState currentState
 +TakeDamage(amount)
 +ChangeState(newState)
 +ApplyBurn(duration)
 +ApplySlow(duration)
 }
 
 class BulletScript {
 +IProjectileEffect ProjectileEffect
 +IBulletVisualDecorator BulletVisualDecorator
 +float Damage
 +GameObject Target
 +Init()
 }
 
 class CannonScript {
 +EffectType SelectedType
 -IProjectileEffect currentEffect
 +SetEffectStrategy(type)
 +Upgrade()
 +CanUpgrade()
 }
 
 class Tower {
 +IProjectileEffect ProjectileEffect
 +FireAt(target)
 +FindTarget()
 }

 %% ===== UI CLASSES =====
 class UpgradeUI {
 +SetTargetCannon(cannon)
 +OnChangeType(type)
 +OnUpgrade()
 }
 
 class TowerSelection {
 +ChangeTowerType(newType)
 +OpenUpgradeUI()
 }

 %% ===== KEY RELATIONSHIPS =====
 EnemyScript --> IEnemyState : \"utilise\"
 EnemyScript --> EnemyManagerScript : \"géré par\"
 
 BulletScript --> IProjectileEffect : \"utilise\"
 BulletScript --> IBulletVisualDecorator : \"utilise\"
 BulletScript --> EnemyScript : \"cible\"
 
 CannonScript --> IProjectileEffect : \"crée\"
 CannonScript --> BulletScript : \"tire\"
 
 Tower --> IProjectileEffect : \"utilise\"
 
 TowerFactory --> CannonScript : \"configure\"
 TowerFactory --> Tower : \"crée\"
 
 TowerSelection --> TowerFactory : \"utilise\"
 TowerSelection --> UpgradeUI : \"ouvre\"
 
 UpgradeUI --> CannonScript : \"améliore\"
 
 GameManager --> Pool : \"utilise\"
 Pool --> BulletScript : \"gère\"
 Pool --> EnemyScript : \"gère\"

 "data": "@startuml TowerDefenseClassDiagram

!theme plain
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

package \"Strategy Pattern - Projectile Effects\" {
 interface IProjectileEffect {
 +ApplyEffect(enemy: EnemyScript, bullet: BulletScript): void
 }
 
 class FireEffect {
 +ApplyEffect(enemy: EnemyScript, bullet: BulletScript): void
 }
 
 class IceEffect {
 +ApplyEffect(enemy: EnemyScript, bullet: BulletScript): void
 }
 
 class WindEffect {
 +ApplyEffect(enemy: EnemyScript, bullet: BulletScript): void
 }
 
 IProjectileEffect <|.. FireEffect
 IProjectileEffect <|.. IceEffect
 IProjectileEffect <|.. WindEffect
}

package \"State Pattern - Enemy States\" {
 interface IEnemyState {
 +Enter(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +Update(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +Exit(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +OnHit(enemy: EnemyScript, damage: float): void
 }
 
 class NormalState {
 +Enter(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +Update(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +Exit(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +OnHit(enemy: EnemyScript, damage: float): void
 }
 
 class BurnedState {
 -duration: float
 -tick: float
 -timer: float
 -tickTimer: float
 -burnDamage: float
 -previousState: IEnemyState
 +BurnedState(burnDamage: float, previousState: IEnemyState)
 +Enter(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +Update(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +Exit(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +OnHit(enemy: EnemyScript, damage: float): void
 }
 
 class FrozenState {
 -duration: float
 -timer: float
 -slowFactor: float
 -previousState: IEnemyState
 +FrozenState(previousState: IEnemyState)
 +Enter(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +Update(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +Exit(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +OnHit(enemy: EnemyScript, damage: float): void
 }
 
 class WindState {
 -duration: float
 -timer: float
 -speedMultiplier: float
 -previousState: IEnemyState
 +WindState(previousState: IEnemyState)
 +Enter(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +Update(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +Exit(enemy: EnemyScript): void
 +OnHit(enemy: EnemyScript, damage: float): void
 }
 
 IEnemyState <|.. NormalState
 IEnemyState <|.. BurnedState
 IEnemyState <|.. FrozenState
 IEnemyState <|.. WindState
}

package \"Decorator Pattern - Bullet Visuals\" {
 interface IBulletVisualDecorator {
 +ApplyVisual(bullet: BulletScript): void
 }
 
 class FireBulletVisualDecorator {
 +ApplyVisual(bullet: BulletScript): void
 }
 
 class IceBulletVisualDecorator {
 +ApplyVisual(bullet: BulletScript): void
 }
 
 class WindBulletVisualDecorator {
 +ApplyVisual(bullet: BulletScript): void
 }
 
 IBulletVisualDecorator <|.. FireBulletVisualDecorator
 IBulletVisualDecorator <|.. IceBulletVisualDecorator
 IBulletVisualDecorator <|.. WindBulletVisualDecorator
}

package \"Factory Pattern - Tower Creation\" {
 class TowerFactory <<static>> {
 +{static} CreateTower(type: TowerType, position: Vector3): GameObject
 +{static} TransformTower(tower: GameObject, newType: TowerType): void
 +{static} GetTowerName(type: TowerType): string
 +{static} GetTowerBaseCost(type: TowerType): int
 +{static} GetAvailableTowerTypes(): TowerType[]
 -{static} ConfigureTower(tower: GameObject, type: TowerType): void
 -{static} SetTowerColor(tower: GameObject, color: Color): void
 }
 
 enum TowerType {
 Fire
 Ice
 Wind
 Basic
 }
 
 TowerFactory --> TowerType : uses
}

package \"Singleton Pattern - Game Managers\" {
 class GameManager <<Singleton>> {
 -{static} gameManagerInstance: GameManager
 +{static} Instance: GameManager
 +Money: int
 +Level: int
 +WavesSurvived: int
 -money: int
 -turretPrice: int
 -rocketPrice: int
 +EnemyEscaped(enemy: GameObject): void
 +EnemyKilled(enemy: GameObject): void
 +TurretBuilt(turret: GameObject): void
 +OnNewWaveStart(waveNumber: int): void
 +GameOver(): void
 +AddMoney(value: int): void
 +GetMoney(): int
 +EnoughMoneyForTurret(tag: string): bool
 +MoneyForTurret(tag: string): int
 }
 
 class EnemyManagerScript <<Singleton>> {
 -{static} enemyManagerInstance: EnemyManagerScript
 +{static} Instance: EnemyManagerScript
 -enemies: Dictionary<GameObject, EnemyDistancePair>
 +RegisterEnemy(enemy: GameObject): void
 +DeleteEnemy(enemy: GameObject): void
 +UpdateEnemy(enemy: GameObject, distance: float): void
 +GetEnemyInRange(position: Vector2, range: float, enemyTags: IEnumerable<string>): GameObject
 +GetClosestEnemyInRange(position: Vector2, range: float, enemyTags: IEnumerable<string>): GameObject
 }
 
 class Pool <<Singleton>> {
 -{static} poolInstance: Pool
 +{static} Instance: Pool
 -pooledObjects: Dictionary<string, GameObject>
 -pool: Dictionary<string, Queue<GameObject>>
 +RegisterObject(prototype: GameObject): void
 +ActivateObject(tag: string): GameObject
 +DeactivateObject(item: GameObject): void
 }
 
 class CameraShaker <<Singleton>> {
 -{static} cameraShakerInstance: CameraShaker
 +{static} Instance: CameraShaker
 +Speed: float
 +Amount: float
 +Decay: float
 -strength: float
 -originalPosition: Vector3
 +Shake(): void
 }
}

package \"Core Game Classes\" {
 class EnemyScript {
 +MaxHealth: float
 +Money: int
 +Coin: GameObject
 +SpawnedCoinMean: float
 +SpawnedCoinStd: float
 -canvas: Transform
 -healthBar: Slider
 -health: float
 -currentState: IEnemyState
 -baseSpeed: float
 -spriteRenderer: SpriteRenderer
 -originalColor: Color
 +TakeDamage(amount: float): void
 +TakeDamageInternal(amount: float): void
 +ChangeState(newState: IEnemyState): void
 +SetSpeedFactor(factor: float): void
 +SetSpeedToBase(): void
 +ApplyBurn(duration: float, damagePerSecond: float): void
 +ApplySlow(duration: float, slowFactor: float): void
 +ApplyWind(duration: float, speedMultiplier: float): void
 +ApplyKnockback(from: Vector2, force: float): void
 +SetColorByEffect(effect: EffectColorType): void
 +ResetColor(): void
 +IsDead(): bool
 }
 
 abstract class FlyingShotScript {
 +Speed: float
 +Direction: Vector2
 +Target: GameObject
 +Range: float
 +Damage: float
 +EnemyTags: List<string>
 +Turret: Transform
 +{abstract} BlowUp(): void
 }
 
 class BulletScript {
 +ProjectileEffect: IProjectileEffect
 +BulletVisualDecorator: IBulletVisualDecorator
 +Direction: Vector2
 +Speed: float
 +Range: float
 +Damage: float
 +Target: GameObject
 +EnemyTags: List<string>
 +Turret: Transform
 +EffectTypeTag: CannonScript.EffectType
 -distance: float
 +Init(): void
 }
 
 class RocketScript {
 +Inertia: float
 +InitialAcceleration: float
 +ShadowOffset: Vector2
 -velocity: Vector2
 -acceleration: float
 -shadow: Transform
 -startTime: float
 +BlowUp(): void
 }
 
 class CannonScript {
 +BulletPrototype: GameObject
 +Enemies: List<GameObject>
 +upgrades: List<TowerUpgradeData>
 +currentLevel: int
 +SelectedType: EffectType
 -ShootingPeriod: float
 -Range: float
 -BulletSpeed: float
 -Damage: float
 -RotationSpeed: float
 -currentEffect: IProjectileEffect
 -bulletPlaceholder: GameObject
 -timeToShoot: float
 -enemyTags: List<string>
 +RangeValue: float
 +DamageValue: float
 +ShootingPeriodValue: float
 +BulletSpeedValue: float
 +RotationSpeedValue: float
 +SetEffectStrategy(type: EffectType): void
 +SetTowerType(type: TowerFactory.TowerType): void
 +CanUpgrade(): bool
 +GetNextUpgradeCost(): int
 +Upgrade(): void
 -ApplyUpgrade(level: int): void
 -TurnToEnemy(position: Vector2): void
 }
 
 class Tower {
 +Damage: int
 +Range: float
 +FireRate: float
 +BulletPrefab: GameObject
 +ProjectileEffect: IProjectileEffect
 -fireCooldown: float
 +FireAt(target: GameObject): void
 +FindTarget(): GameObject
 }
 
 class TowerInfo {
 -towerType: TowerFactory.TowerType
 -towerName: string
 -baseCost: int
 -creationTime: float
 +TowerType: TowerFactory.TowerType
 +TowerName: string
 +BaseCost: int
 +CreationTime: float
 +SetTowerType(type: TowerFactory.TowerType, name: string, cost: int): void
 +GetDescription(): string
 }
 
 class TowerSelection {
 +upgradeUIPrefab: GameObject
 -currentUI: GameObject
 -isSelectable: bool
 +HandleMouseClick(): void
 +OpenUpgradeUI(): void
 +ChangeTowerType(newType: TowerFactory.TowerType): void
 +CloseUI(): void
 }
 
 class TowerVisuals {
 -baseRenderer: SpriteRenderer
 -cannonRenderer: SpriteRenderer
 -fireBaseSprite: Sprite
 -fireCannonSprite: Sprite
 -iceBaseSprite: Sprite
 -iceCannonSprite: Sprite
 -windBaseSprite: Sprite
 -windCannonSprite: Sprite
 -basicBaseSprite: Sprite
 -basicCannonSprite: Sprite
 +SetVisuals(type: TowerType): void
 }
 
 class TowerUpgradeData {
 +level: int
 +upgradeCost: int
 +damage: float
 +range: float
 +shootingPeriod: float
 +bulletSpeed: float
 +rotationSpeed: float
 }
 
 class EnemySpawner {
 +Waves: List<Wave>
 -waveIndex: int
 -currentWave: Wave
 -spawnTime: float
 -difficultyLevel: int
 -Spawn(prototype: GameObject): void
 }
 
 class Wave {
 +Amount: int
 +Enemy: GameObject
 +SpawnTime: float
 +RestTime: float
 +InitialAmount: int
 +InitialRestTime: float
 +InitialSpawnTime: float
 }
 
 class PathFollower {
 +Type: PathType
 +Speed: float
 +OffsetAmount: float
 -PositionOffset: Vector2
 -path: Path
 -segmentIndex: int
 -A: Vector2
 -B: Vector2
 -C: Vector2
 -D: Vector2
 -v1: Vector2
 -v2: Vector2
 -v3: Vector2
 -t: float
 -knockbackPause: float
 +PauseForKnockback(duration: float): void
 -RecomputeSegment(): void
 }
}

package \"UI Classes\" {
 class UpgradeUI {
 +fireButton: Button
 +iceButton: Button
 +windButton: Button
 +closeButton: Button
 +upgradeButton: Button
 +upgradeCostText: Text
 +towerInfoText: Text
 -targetCannon: CannonScript
 -selector: TowerSelection
 +SetTargetCannon(cannon: CannonScript, selection: TowerSelection): void
 +OnChangeType(type: TowerFactory.TowerType): void
 +RefreshUpgradeButton(): void
 +RefreshTowerInfo(): void
 +OnUpgrade(): void
 +CloseUI(): void
 }
 
 class BuildLocationScript {
 +{static} OpenCanvas: GameObject
 -canvas: GameObject
 -turret: GameObject
 -pressed: bool
 }
 
 class BuildMenuItemScript {
 +BaseSprite: Sprite
 +HoverSprite: Sprite
 +ClickSprite: Sprite
 +Prototype: GameObject
 +towerType: TowerFactory.TowerType
 +useFactory: bool
 -text: Text
 -price: Text
 -parent: GameObject
 -rangeSprite: GameObject
 -range: float
 -image: Image
 -pressed: bool
 -disabled: bool
 }
}

package \"Utility Classes\" {
 class AutoDisableScript {
 +TimeOut: float
 -remainingTime: float
 }
 
 class CoinScript {
 +{static} Value: int
 -randomNumber: float
 }
 
 class ExplosionScript {
 -particleSystem: ParticleSystem
 }
 
 class SoundEffectScript {
 -audio: AudioSource
 }
 
 class HealthDrawerScript {
 +FullHeart: Sprite
 +EmptyHeart: Sprite
 +HeartObjects: GameObject[]
 -Hearts: Image[]

 }
 
 class MoneyDrawer {
 +TextFieldObject: GameObject
 -text: Text
 +Draw(money: int): void
 }
}

' === RELATIONSHIPS ===

' State Pattern Relationships
EnemyScript --> IEnemyState : currentState
EnemyScript --> EnemyManagerScript : managed by

' Strategy Pattern Relationships
BulletScript --> IProjectileEffect : ProjectileEffect
CannonScript --> IProjectileEffect : currentEffect
Tower --> IProjectileEffect : ProjectileEffect

' Decorator Pattern Relationships
BulletScript --> IBulletVisualDecorator : BulletVisualDecorator

' Factory Pattern Relationships
TowerFactory --> CannonScript : configures
TowerFactory --> TowerVisuals : configures
TowerFactory --> TowerInfo : configures

' Core Game Relationships
CannonScript --> TowerUpgradeData : upgrades
CannonScript --> BulletScript : creates
CannonScript --> EnemyScript : targets

Tower --> BulletScript : creates

TowerSelection --> TowerFactory : uses
TowerSelection --> UpgradeUI : creates
TowerSelection --> CannonScript : manages

UpgradeUI --> CannonScript : upgrades
UpgradeUI --> TowerSelection : communicates
UpgradeUI --> TowerFactory : uses

EnemySpawner --> Wave : contains
EnemySpawner --> EnemyScript : spawns
EnemySpawner --> GameManager : notifies

GameManager --> Pool : uses
GameManager --> CameraShaker : uses

Pool --> BulletScript : manages
Pool --> EnemyScript : manages

PathFollower --> EnemyScript : moves

' Inheritance Relationships
FlyingShotScript <|-- BulletScript
FlyingShotScript <|-- RocketScript

BuildMenuItemScript --> TowerFactory : uses
